Purpose of Ubuntu 2
Ubuntu 2 acts as the Security Monitoring Server in the SOC Lab. It hosts Suricata IDS for network threat detection and Splunk Universal Forwarder for log forwarding. Suricata generates security alerts and network activity logs, which are forwarded to Splunk SIEM for centralized monitoring, investigation, dashboard creation, and threat detection.

